##It's a playground everywhere

Micro-signal Yeguangbeifukan

Function introduction the supplement of Xinmin Evening News, founded on May 1,1946, is the oldest comprehensive supplement of Chinese newspapers.

###Yoga, lunges, planks... during the epidemic, reduce travel, indoor and family members together fancy fitness, to stay healthy, long skills, but also enhance the relationship.

###

###Has returned to work. When I think back to my days at home, it was my playground.

February 4, my husband and I returned from home to Shanghai, as required by the two of us to observe a period of time at home. At first I thought it was beautiful, then I collapsed in bed and started to party on my phone. Until a sitting up on the back pain, turn over the intensity index of the three stars of the movement. In order not to let oneself degenerate down, also in order to find some boring way, I bitterly regret, decided to take the "home health miss" line, during the epidemic, self-entertainment and can be strong and healthy.

The habit of doing yoga for many years has made me feel sick every day without breaking myself. Yoga stretching base, plank support to do auxiliary, from time to time to two bobby jump, but not too loud, can not affect the next-door children online classes.

Exercise Time every day is very particular, either before going to bed, or just woke up, or when the sun is shining. Open the window and let the fresh air rush into the room, squeezing out the carbon dioxide released by the exercise. A few times my husband saw me pull myself up so seriously, and came along for the ride. Just as the evening news was putting out some home sports videos, which were of moderate intensity and easy to use, I recommended them to him. Let him stretch while touching the basketball, it makes up for the fact that he can't go out for days. Occasionally a few interactions, back stretch, and foot pressure, I bounce him high, and some merciless ridicule, so happy day passed.

However, these "standing still" type of exercise time is far longer than lying in bed, so I adjust the strategy, open up territory, the kitchen, balcony, bathroom as a place to exercise. I have a weird habit of washing my face and brushing my teeth at the same time, which is sort of a mental cue, like I'm earning double my value in a period of time. Thus, to make full use of this mentality, morning and evening washing content is more and more rich: while brushing my teeth while kicking my legs behind, when washing my face to adopt a straight waist squat posture; since watching a star fitness reality show, I have learned to apply a mask horse step therapy, he thinks he has a theory: the Lower Disk is stretched, deep breathing, let the Qi and blood gradually up, and then stimulate blood circulation in the face, pores open, good for water and nutrients to fully absorb... ... ... The husband leans on the side shaking his head to comment: This theory is a bit crooked, and a little open-minded. I enjoyed it. I enjoyed it.

As a new kitchen, basic on weekdays by the unit canteen plus take-away to solve two meals. Special period, my husband and I encourage each other, follow the principle of staying at home. As a result, the stove and the exhaust hood were forced to open, and cooking, washing the dishes, and fruit were on my daily list of major activities, in large quantities and in small amounts: Washing one more bowl than yesterday, for example, could be considered a sign of increased physical fitness. In this self deprecating, oh no, self inspiring atmosphere, a third of the food in the House has been consumed in just a few days, along with a supply of dry food from home; one kitchen Lin Bai has given up takeout and driven all the way up the food chain, to be the new kitchen star. Not only that, the two of US worked separately, I prepared his spoons, I washed the dishes and he cleaned the battlefield, not only to a certain extent, we avoided the situation of turning into a period of fatigue due to the momentum of the movement, it also effectively reduces the possibility of unintentional hurt feelings caused by mutual complaints.

The utilization rate of the balcony is greatly improved. The Sun father-in-law a face, I would like to rush to the balcony bask in the West. The husband really can not bear to see, a face wry smile said: You put the quilt, every day so bask, the quilt will also bask in Baldness. I said, you know what, washing clothes, drying coats, drying the quilt, which is not labor-intensive ah! It's my daily physical fitness workout. Moreover, the fight against the epidemic, everyone has the responsibility to fight the virus from the Sun Quilt to do! With that, I handed him the clothesline to feel like hanging it out to dry!

After 14 days at home, it's not easy to stay healthy. However, give yourself something to do, heart and family together to do something, both long skills and enhance the relationship, will also reap a lot of unexpected small happiness.
